Sources & Dependencies

Languages & Frameworks
Python 3.10+ (scripting language).
Terraform 1.6+ (infrastructure as code).
Flask (Python web framework, MIT License).
Node.js 18 LTS (for Node detection, MIT License).

Python Packages
typer (CLI framework, MIT License).
jinja2 (templating Terraform and scripts, BSD License).
subprocess (Python stdlib, for running Terraform).
requests (HTTP, Apache 2.0 License).

Infrastructure
AWS EC2 (cloud VM).
Nginx (reverse proxy, BSD License).
Gunicorn (WSGI server for Flask, MIT License).

External References
Terraform AWS Provider Docs: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs
Flask Documentation: https://flask.palletsprojects.com/
Nginx Docs: https://nginx.org/en/docs/
AWS EC2 Docs: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ec2/index.html
